cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper is about speaker recognition, which is related to sound processing.
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper uses deep learning techniques to improve speaker recognition, which is related to natural language processing.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a hybrid system based on deep belief networks and deep neural networks to discriminatively model each target speaker, which is related to machine learning.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although the paper is not directly related to computer vision, the techniques used in speaker recognition can be applied to other areas of pattern recognition.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses deep learning techniques to improve speaker recognition, which is related to artificial intelligence.
